VisAD Tutorial example 4_01 Like example 3_09 but using a 3D display We have the functions altitude = h(latitude, longitude) temperature = f(latitude, longitude) represented by the MathType ( (latitude, longitude) -> (altitude, temperature ) ) Map the altitude to ZAxis and temperature to RGB Run program with "java P4_01"
